GET info about SpaceX capsules

Source: R/get_SpaceX_capsules.R
get_SpaceX_capsules.Rd

GET info about SpaceX capsules

get_SpaceX_capsules(type = NULL, ...)

Arguments

type

character: type of the request: Choose between "upcoming" or "past".
...

: Query string to API. See more in details.

Value

data.frame with parsed data from SpaceX API.

Examples


# get all capsules
get_SpaceX_capsules()
